window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>In the year 2057, the world has become a corporate-run utopia for the super-rich, and a hellhole for all the rest.</b></p> <p>Catherine \"Cat\" Leblanc is an orphan that is about as far from super-rich as one can be. When the Incursion alarms start blaring and the sky starts raining hungry xenos, it's just another blemish on an already piss-poor afternoon.</p> <p><i>Stray Cat Strut</i> is a cyberpunk magical-girl alien-invasion LitRPG that's exactly as wild as it sounds.</p>"; 
